node.text: One of the most useful shots you will ever learn! Knowing how to hit a bump and run will save you so many shots on your rounds. Once you get the technique down, it’s all about club selection so practice, practice, practice! Let me know if you have any questions😌

node.text:
Woods, hybrids, or long irons? 🤷‍♀️ People ask me all the time which type of clubs they should play and it’s a tricky question because it’s so individual for everyone and can be confusing. I was never a fan of long irons and found them hard to fit so I always played hybrids but recently just switched that out for a 5 wood! What do you prefer?

I went to @clubchampion where they answered all of my questions and gave me great tips. I’m sharing that all on my latest YouTube!

Book your fitting with the link in bio and use code PAIGE21 for 20% off with an equipment purchase!

I’m such a baby when it comes to bad weather and golf now. That’s why you’ll find me at @xgolfamerica anytime there’s not perfect golf weather😂 What are you up to this weekend? Playing any golf?

node.text:
Play a hole with me! 

Patty Jewett is one of my favorite munis for many reasons. Right after college I had no direction in my life except I knew I wanted to try to play professional golf. I didn’t have any money so I would practice here. If you scroll back you’ll see majority of my golf videos at this course. It’s crazy that 5 years, over 3 million followers, and a failed pro golf career later this is still my go to course in the springs and I’m still wearing my tank tops haha. Thanks for following me through it all❤️

node.text:
SUMMER GIVEAWAY ☀️ 

If you want to go to the beach with me, this giveaway is for you! 3 winners will get:
👙 A limited beach towel featuring a never before seen picture of me in the bikini I have on here 
🏖 Flagpole-To-Go Beach and Backyard Kit + sports flag of choice
 🕶 Pair of Nectar sunglasses

All you have to do is like this photo and FOLLOW @flagpoletogo to be entered to win! 

Flagpole-To-Go is a must have this summer if you want to rep your team. If you don’t live by the beach like me, you can easily set it up in your backyard. 

And for those asking, yes there are more golf towels coming sometime soon, but this is your only chance to be first and get this beach towel😏

Want to play a round of golf with me? Now you can!

It’s that easy! See you on the course😍 Winner will be picked June 30th.

node.text:
Not every shot is a good one but you always have to play it off for the gram😎 side note ball grabbers are cool. Yeah I said it. 

I’m sorry I’m not there to grab your balls but you can get your own Ball Grabber from the link in my bio🙌🏻
